Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20get%20yourself%20that%20much%20more%20time%20to%20get%20into%20the%20rhythm%20because%20you%20have%20not%20got%20the%20runs.%20Your%20bowlers%20haven't%20got%20the%20rhythm.%20There%20are%20others%20too%20who%20need%20time%20in%20the%20middle%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20optional%20practice%20session%20is%20something%20that%20I%20don't%20believe.%20The%20decision%20for%20optional%20training%20should%20rest%20with%20the%20captain%20and%20the%20coach.%20The%20coach%20should%20say%2C%20'Hey%2C%20you%20hit%20150%2C%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20come%20to%20practice.%20Hey%2C%20you%20bowled%2040%20overs%20in%20the%20match%2C%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20come%20to%20practice.'%20They%20should%20not%20be%20given%20the%20option.%20If%20you%20give%20the%20players%20that%20option%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20them%2C%20especially%20the%20certainties%2C%20will%20say%2C%20'No%2C%20I%20am%20going%20to%20stay%20in%20my%20room.'%20And%20that's%20not%20what%20Indian%20cricket%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaintaining%20a%20morally%20high%20stance%20on%20the%20subject%2C%20Gavaskar%20reminded%20Indian%20cricketers%20that%20playing%20for%20the%20country%20is%20an%20honour%20and%20privilege.%20Hence%2C%20players%20shouldn't%20shy%20away%20from%20dedicating%20themselves%20in%20the%20service%20of%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndian%20cricket%20needs%20people%20who%20are%20totally%20dedicated%20to%20their%20cause.%20It's%20an%20honour%20and%20privilege%20to%20be%20playing%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20counted%20the%20number%20of%20days%20they%20will%20be%20here.%20It's%2057%20days%20in%20Australia.%20Out%20of%20those%2057%2C%20if%20you%20count%20out%20five%20matches%2C%20then%20you%20are%20left%20with%2032%20days%2C%20two%20matches%20for%20the%20PM%20XI.%20Thirty%20days%2C%20they%20were%20going%20to%20get%20off.%20They%20had%20one%20extra%20day%20off%20in%20Perth%2C%20now%20two%20in%20Adelaide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGavaskar%2C%20however%2C%20allowed%20the%20marquee%20trio%20of%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jasprit%20Bumrah%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1724-jasprit-bumrah-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%20to%20miss%20the%20practice%20sessions%20if%20they%20wanted%20to%20because%20of%20their%20'experience'.%20However%2C%20he%20does%20want%20the%20youngsters%20to%20get%20more%20sessions%20under%20their%20belt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20request%20to%20them%20is%20to%20please%20come%20and%20practice.%20Again%2C%20Bumrah%20doesn't%20have%20to%20practice.%20If%20Rohit%20and%20Virat%20don't%20have%20to%20practice%2C%20that's%20fine%2C%20because%20they%20are%20experienced%20players.%20Let%20the%20others%20come%20out%20and%20practice%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733709840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fdg7gj3v_virat-kohli-and-rohit-sharma-afp_625x300_08_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-vs-india-2024-25%2Fcant-sit-in-hotel-room-sunil-gavaskars-blunt-message-to-rohit-kohli-and-others-7200043%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Both%20Virat%20Kohli%20and%20Rohit%20Sharma%20flopped%20with%20the%20bat%20as%20India%20suffered%20a%2010-wicket%20defeat%20against%20Australia%20in%20Adelaide.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Josh%20Allen%20makes%20NFL%20history%20with%206%20TDs%20against%20Rams%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733709611000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116120428%2Cimgsize-49562.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fnfl%2Fnews%2Fjosh-allen-makes-nfl-history-with-6-tds-against-rams-strengthens-mvp-case-despite-narrow-44-42-loss%2Farticleshow%2F