%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20military%20struck%20ISIS%20targets%20in%20Syria%20on%20Sunday%20as%20rebel%20groups%20toppled%20the%20government.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELongtime%20Syrian%20leader%20Bashar%20Assad%20fled%20Damascus%20for%20Moscow.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%20said%20US%20forces%20would%20remain%20in%20Syria%20to%20fight%20ISIS.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20military%20said%20it%20carried%20out%20dozens%20of%20precision%20strikes%20against%20ISIS%20targets%20in%20central%20Syria%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20widespread%20airstrikes%20came%20after%20a%20dayslong%20blitz%20by%20rebel%20forces%20that%20ultimately%20led%20to%20the%20downfall%20of%20Syria's%20longtime%20leader%2C%20Bashar%20Assad.%20Russian%20state%20news%20media%20reported%20Sunday%20that%20Assad%20had%20arrived%20in%20Moscow%2C%20where%20he%20was%20given%20asylum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20Central%20Command%2C%20which%20oversees%20Middle%20East%20operations%2C%20said%20it%20struck%20ISIS%20leaders%2C%20operatives%2C%20and%20camps%20to%20prevent%20the%20terrorist%20group%20from%20rebuilding%20in%20central%20Syria%20amid%20the%20chaos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECentcom%20said%20it%20used%20US%20Air%20Force%20B-52%20bombers%2C%20F-15%20fighter%20jets%2C%20and%20A-10%20attack%20aircraft%20to%20strike%20over%2075%20targets%2C%20adding%20that%20battle%20damage%20assessments%20are%20underway.%20A%20senior%20administration%20official%2C%20speaking%20to%20reporters%2C%20described%20the%20operation%20as%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20about%20140%20munitions%20were%20used.%20It%20is%20unclear%20what%20missiles%20or%20bombs%20may%20have%20been%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20should%20be%20no%20doubt%20%E2%80%94%20we%20will%20not%20allow%20ISIS%20to%20reconstitute%20and%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20current%20situation%20in%20Syria%2C%26quot%3B%20Gen.%20Michael%20Erik%20Kurilla%2C%20the%20Centcom%20commander%2C%20said%20i