rael%20and%20Iran%20has%20been%20a%20source%20of%20concern%20and%20some%20of%20India's%20diplomatic%20efforts%20are%20focused%20on%20that%20aspect%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20address%20at%20the%20Manama%20Dialogue%20in%20Bahrain%2C%20S%20Jaishankar%2C%20without%20directly%20referring%20to%20attacks%20on%20commercial%20ships%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20by%20Houthi%20operators%2C%20said%20India%20has%20an%20interest%20in%20trying%20to%20mitigate%20the%20security%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES%20Jaishankar%2C%20on%20a%20two-day%20visit%20to%20Bahrain%20from%20Saturday%2C%20touched%20upon%20various%20issues%2C%20including%20how%20to%20prevent%20conflicts%20from%20spreading%20further%2C%20the%20importance%20of%20key%20connectivity%20projects%20and%20the%20need%20to%20improve%20the%20security%20situation%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20recent%20times%2C%20for%20all%20of%20us%2C%20the%20relationship%20or%20absence%20of%20it%20between%20Israel%20and%20Iran%20has%20been%20particularly%20a%20source%20of%20concern%2C%20so%20some%20of%20our%20diplomatic%20efforts%20has%20focused%20on%20that%20particular%20aspect%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20external%20affairs%20minister%2C%20however%2C%20did%20not%20elaborate%20on%20India's%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20mounting%20global%20concerns%20over%20escalating%20tensions%20between%20Iran%20and%20Israel%20in%20the%20last%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20Iran%20fired%20around%20200%20missiles%20into%20Israel%20in%20response%20to%20Israel's%20killing%20of%20Hezbollah%20chief%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%20and%20other%20commanders%20of%20the%20operator%20outfit.%20Israel%20subsequently%20retaliated%20against%20the%20Iranian%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20external%20affairs%20minister%2C%20talking%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20West%20Asia%20for%20New%20Delhi%2C%20also%20highlighted%20India's%20sustained%20economic%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20today%20almost%20a%20USD%204%20trillion%20economy%2C%20(and)%20we%20expect%20to%20comfortably%20double%20that%20this%20decade.%20Our%20trade%20is%20today%20around%20USD%20800%20billion%2C%20that%20too%20should%20at%20least%20double%20this%20decade%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20I%20again%20cannot%20overstate%20the%20stakes%20that%20we%20have%20because%20this%20region%20is%20the%20immediate%20for%20us%20the%20world%20beyond%20our%20borders%20that%20immediately%20awaits%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20remarks%2C%20S%20Jaishankar%20also%20referred%20to%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20and%20said%20the%20security%20domain%20is%20a%20key%20area%20for%20strategic%20regional%20cooperation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20we%20have%20had%20very%20significant%20security%20challenges%20in%20this%20area%20with%20a%20very%20deep%20and%20disastrous%20impact%20for%20trade%20in%20Asia%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20when%20we%20look%20at%20the%20diversion%20of%20maritime%20routes%20and%20the%20insurance%20costs%2C%20and%20the%20shipping%20costs%20and%20the%20container%20costs%20and%20the%20delay%20that%20it%20has%20imposed%2C%20obviously%2C%20you%20know%2C%20India%2C%20but%20not%20just%20India%2C%20we%20have%20an%20interest%20in%20trying%20to%20mitigate%20that%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20view%20of%20the%20volatile%20situation%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%2C%20shipments%20were%20diverted%20to%20other%20routes%20that%20had%20increased%20the%20cost%20of%20transportation%20significantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20external%20affairs%20minister%20also%20briefly%20spoke%20about%20India's%20naval%20presence%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20actually%20had%20a%20naval%20presence%20in%20this%20region%20in%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Aden%2C%20Somalia%2C%20Northern%20Arabian%20Sea.%20Over%20the%20year%20it's%20been%20roughly%20about%2030%20ships%2C%20the%20peak%20was%20about%2012%20ships%20at%20one%20point%20of%20time%20which%20were%20deployed%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20in%20the%20last%20year%2C%20we%20have%20actually%20responded%20to%2024%20actual%20incidents%2C%20escorted%20250%20ships%2C%20rescued%20120%20crew%20members.%20So%20we%20are%20making%20our%20contributions%2C%20we%20working%20in%20tandem%20with%20Operation%20Prosperity%20Guardian.%20We%20have%20our%20own%20nationally%20named%20operation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Operation%20Prosperity%20Guardian'%20is%20a%20US-led%20military%20mission%20that%20was%20launched%20late%20last%20year%20to%20jointly%20address%20security%20challenges%20in%20the%20southern%20Red%20Sea%20and%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Aden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES%20Jaishankar%20said%20India%20intends%20to%20increase%20its%20bilateral%20exercise%20both%20in%20the%20Gulf%20with%20its%20partners%20as%20well%20as%20in%20the%20Mediterranean.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20in%20the%20Gulf%2C%20I%20think%20the%20Gulf%20countries%20have%20been%20our%20fairly%20regular%20partners%20by%20now%20and%20in%20almost%20every%20case%20we%20have%20seen%20an%20uptick%20in%20our%20shared%20activities%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20Mediterranean%2C%20particularly%2C%20apart%20from%20Israel%2C%20with%20Greece%2C%20with%20Egypt%2C%20we%20have%20had%20significant%20exercises%20this%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES%20Jaishankar%20also%20elaborated%20on%20various%20connectivity%20projects%2C%20including%20the%20India-Myanmar-Thailand%20Trilateral%20(IMTT)%20highway%2C%20the%20International%20North-South%20Transport%20Corridor%20(INSTC)%20and%20the%20ambitious%20India-Middle%20East-Europe%20Economic%20Corridor%20(IMEEC)%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20fact%2C%20one%20day%2C%20when%20these%20corridors%20are%20done%2C%20the%20IMEC%20will%20bring%20the%20Atlantic%20to%20India%2C%20the%20IMTT%20will%20actually%20take%20that%20connectivity%20from%20India%20to%20the%20Pacific%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20you%20can%20actually%20envisage%20a%20connectivity%20corridor%20from%20the%20Atlantic%20to%20the%20Pacific%20going%20through%20southern%20Europe%2C%20going%20through%20the%20Arabian%20peninsula%2C%20cutting%20through%20the%20southern%20part%20of%20the%20Asian%20continent.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BSo%20this%20truly%20has%20a%20game-changing%20possibility.%20But%20like%20everything%20game-changing%2C%20this%20needs%20obviously%20a%20lot%20of%20hard%20work%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20resources%20and%20many%20obstacles%20to%20overcome%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733677260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Ffa8mkhl8_s-jaishankar_625x300_08_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Firan-israel-relationship-or-absence-of-it-source-of-concern-s-jaishankar-7202702%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20relationship%20or%20absence%20of%20it%20between%20Israel%20and%20Iran%20has%20been%20a%20source%20of%20concern%20and%20some%20of%20India's%20diplomatic%20efforts%20are%20focused%20on%20that%20aspect%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20on%20Sunday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mystery%20Surrounds%20Whereabouts%20Of%20Assad%2C%20Who%20Boarded%20Flight%20From%20Syria%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMystery%20surrounded%20the%20whereabouts%20of%20Bashar%20al-Assad%2C%20who%20was%20no%20longer%20in%20Damascus%20when%20rebels%20captured%20the%20Syria