ce%20Department%20monitors%20in%20its%20%26quot%3Blawful%20intercept%26quot%3B%20system.%20The%20lawful%20intercept%20system%20is%20what%20allows%20law%20enforcement%2C%20through%20a%20court%20order%2C%20to%20wiretap%20or%20%26quot%3Bbug%26quot%3B%20phone%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FBI%20warned%20that%20all%20US%20citizens%20should%20use%20a%20cellphone%20that%20automatically%20updates%20its%20operating%20system%20and%20use%20encryption%20and%20multifactor%20authentication%20for%20email%20and%20social%20media%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeuberger%20said%20in%20an%20earlier%20press%20call%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20the%20government%20does%20not%20believe%20any%20of%20the%20targeted%20telecom%20companies%20have%20%26quot%3Bfully%20removed%26quot%3B%20the%20Chinese%20hackers%20from%20their%20networks%2C%20and%20communications%20are%20still%20at%20risk.%20Senior%20White%20House%20officials%20on%20the%20call%20said%20the%20hack%20has%20been%20ongoing%20for%20%26quot%3Blikely%20one%20to%20two%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPresident%20Biden%20has%20been%20briefed%20multiple%20times%20on%20this%20compromise%2C%26quot%3B%20Neuberger%20told%20reporters.%20She%20added%20that%20the%20White%20House%20%26quot%3Bhas%20made%20it%20a%20priority%20for%20the%20federal%20government%20to%20do%20everything%20it%20can%20to%20get%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeuberger%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fericgeller%2Fstatus%2F1864409228686897539%3Fs%3D46%26t%3DNui0UmVGijsDXT2qSHv1rQ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhite%20House%20leaders%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20meeting%20three%20times%20a%20week%20to%20discuss%20the%20hack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Senate%20Commerce%20Subcommittee%20will%20hold%20a%20hearing%20on%20December%2011%20to%20discuss%20security%20threats%20to%20communications%20networks%20and%20review%20best%20practices%20for%20providers%20to%20mitigate%20consumer%20risks.%20The%20committee%20will%20focus%20on%20the%20Salt%20Typhoon%20attacks%20in%20the%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-salt-typhoon-hack-china-phone-security-phone-encryption-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733676385000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675208568fb3f94e5073b129%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-salt-typhoon-hack-china-phone-security-phone-encryption-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Salt%20Typhoon%20hack%20originated%20in%20China%20and%20is%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20attacks%20on%20American%20telecom%20companies%20ever%2C%20officials%20say.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kniemeyer%40insider.com%20(Kenneth%20Niemeyer)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-salt-typhoon-hack-china-phone-security-phone-encryption-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Brian%20Thompson%20case%3A%20Nationwide%20manhunt%20for%20UnitedHealthCare%20CEO%E2%80%99s%20killer%20continues%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733676325000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116111645%2Cimgsize-1166709.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fbrian-thompson-case-nationwide-manhunt-for-unitedhealthcare-ceos-killer-continues%2Farticleshow%2F116111326.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F116111326.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EA%20nationwide%20manhunt%20is%20underway%20for%20the%20gunman%20who%20fatally%20shot%20UnitedHealthCare%20CEO%20Brian%20Thompson%20in%20Midtown%20Manhattan.%20The%20suspect%2C%20seen%20fleeing%20on%20an%20electric%20bike%20and%20later%20in%20a%20taxi%2C%20is%20believed%20to%2