%2Fa%3E-led%20Indian%20cricket%20team's%20hopes%20of%20reaching%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20(WTC)%20Final%20suffered%20a%20major%20blow%20after%20a%20humiliating%20loss%20to%20Australia%20in%20the%20pink-ball%20Test%20in%20Adelaide.%20India%20were%20outplayed%20as%20Australia%20went%20on%20to%20clinch%20the%20game%20by%2010%20wickets.%20Following%20this%20loss%2C%20India%20fell%20to%20the%20third%20position%20in%20the%20WTC%20Points%20Table.%20However%2C%20they%20are%20still%20in%20the%20running%20for%20qualification%20and%20there%20remains%20multiple%20scenarios%20that%20can%20see%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20Co%20in%20the%20summit%20clash.%20The%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20cannot%20lose%20any%20more%20matches%20in%20the%20ongoing%20series%20against%20Australia%20to%20keep%20their%20WTC%20Final%20dreams%20alive.%20With%20three%20matches%20remaining%2C%20three%20more%20wins%20for%20India%20will%20guarantee%20their%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20two%20wins%20and%20a%20draw%20can%20also%20make%20sure%20that%20they%20will%20find%20a%20place%20in%20the%20WTC%20Final%20if%20South%20Africa%20win%20the%202nd%20Test%20match%20against%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20India%20lose%20another%20Test%20match%20in%20this%20series%2C%20their%20qualification%20will%20completely%20depend%20on%20the%20results%20in%20the%C2%A0South%20Africa%20vs%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20the%20Sri%20Lanka%20vs%20Australia%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%C2%A0batting%20legend%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sunil%20Gavaskar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F40594-sunil-manohar-gavaskar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESunil%20Gavaskar%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20urged%20India%20not%20to%20%26quot%3Bwaste%26quot%3B%20time%20in%20their%20hotel%20rooms%20after%20the%20early%20finish%20of%20the%20pink%20ball%20Test%2C%20but%20utilise%20the%20two%20extra%20days%20by%20sweating%20it%20out%20in%20training%20so%20they%20can%20bounce%20back%20in%20the%20third%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20were%20thoroughly%20exposed%20in%20their%2010-wicket%20loss%20in%20the%20second%20Test%20of%20the%20Border%20Gavaskar%20Trophy%20with%20the%20match%20ending%20in%20less%20than%20two-and-a-half%20days%20as%20Australia%20bounced%20back%20to%20level%20the%20five-game%20series%201-1.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%20at%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20series%20as%20a%20three-match%20series.%20Forget%20it%20was%20a%20five-Test%20series.%20What%20I%20would%20like%20this%20Indian%20team%20to%20do%20is%20use%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20days%20for%20practice%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20told%20the%20official%20broadcaster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20important.%20You%20can't%20be%20sitting%20in%20your%20hotel%20room%20or%20wherever%20you're%20going%20because%20you%20have%20come%20here%20to%20play%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20have%20to%20practice%20the%20whole%20day.%20You%20can%20practice%20a%20session%20in%20the%20morning%20or%20afternoon%2C%20whichever%20time%20you%20choose%2C%20but%20do%20not%20waste%20these%20days.%20You%20would%20have%20been%20here%20playing%20a%20Test%20match%20if%20the%20Test%20match%20were%20to%20go%20on%20for%20five%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20Test%20begins%20on%20December%2014%20and%20Gavaskar%20said%20the%20Indians%20should%20utilise%20the%20intervening%20time%20to%20get%20their%20rhythm%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20PTI%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733668260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fpc3jguq_sc_625x300_08_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-vs-india-2024-25%2Fhow-can-india-qualify-for-world-test-championship-final-after-loss-vs-australia-in-pink-ball-test-7201891%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Rohit%20Sharma-led%20Indian%20cricket%20team's%20hopes%20of%20reaching%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20(WTC)%20Final%20suffered%20a%20major%20bl