0can%2C%20are%20advised%20to%20leave%20by%20the%20earliest%20available%20commercial%20flights%20and%20others%20are%20requested%20to%20observe%20utmost%20precaution%20about%20their%20safety%20and%20restrict%20their%20movements%20to%20the%20minimum%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20India%20said%20it%20is%20closely%20following%20the%20unfolding%20situation%20in%20Syria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20taken%20note%20of%20the%20recent%20escalation%20in%20fighting%20in%20the%20north%20of%20Syria.%20We%20are%20closely%20following%20the%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20MEA%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20about%2090%20Indian%20nationals%20in%20Syria%2C%20including%2014%20who%20are%20working%20in%20various%20UN%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESyria's%20rebels%20said%20the%20leader%20of%20Islamist%20group%20Hayat%20Tahrir%20al-Sham%2C%20Abu%20Mohammed%20al-Jolani%2C%20arrived%20in%20Damascus%20hours%20after%20fighters%20seized%20the%20capital%20and%20said%20they%20ousted%20President%20Bashar%20al-Assad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIdentifying%20him%20by%20his%20real%20name%20Ahmed%20al-Sharaa%2C%20the%20statement%20on%20Telegram%20said%20he%20had%20%26quot%3Bknelt%20down%20prostrating%20to%20God%20in%20thanks%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20ground%20after%20arriving%20in%20the%20Syrian%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20showed%20him%20kneeling%20in%20a%20field%20and%20bringing%20his%20head%20to%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESyrians%20woke%20up%20to%20a%20changed%20country%20on%20Sunday%2C%20as%20rebels%20swept%20into%20Damascus%20less%20than%20two%20weeks%20into%20a%20lightning%20offensive%20declaring%20they%20had%20toppled%20%26quot%3Btyrant%26quot%3B%20Assad%2C%20whose%20whereabouts%20are%20unknown%20after%20he%20reportedly%20fled%20Syria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20statement%20that%20was%20read%20on%20Syrian%20state%20television%2C%20which%20rebels%20took%20over%2C%20quoted%20Jolani%20as%20saying