0smaller%20than%20I'd%20hoped%20for%2C%20especially%20given%20its%20%2422%20price%20tag.%20But%20any%20complaints%20I%20had%20quickly%20vanished%20when%20our%20server%20arrived%20to%20pour%20papaya%20dressing%20over%20the%20flower-adorned%20salad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20thick%20papaya%20sauce%20was%20flavored%20with%20garlic%20and%20chiles%20%E2%80%94%20the%20same%20mixture%20used%20in%20the%20hot%20sauce%20that%20Andrea%20had%20already%20brought%20to%20our%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sauce%20helped%20accentuate%20bites%20of%20cucumber%2C%20tomato%2C%20cape%20gooseberries%2C%20and%20grapes%2C%20along%20with%20the%20almond-butter-filled%20avocado%20half.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20salad's%20balance%20between%20creamy%20and%20crunchy%20textures%20and%20spicy%20and%20sweet%20flavors%20made%20it%20extremely%20compelling.%20Once%20I'd%20eaten%20all%20that%20I%20could%20with%20my%20fork%2C%20I%20spooned%20the%20remnants%20into%20my%20mouth%2C%20savoring%20every%20last%20bite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20favorite%20dish%20was%20the%20chicken%20and%20rice.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20plate%20of%20chicken%20and%20orange%20rice%20with%20greens%20and%20onion%20to%20garnish%20the%20dish.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673bb579fa0140cdd5642a25%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20loved%20all%20the%20different%20flavors%20of%20the%20chicken%20and%20rice.%3Cp%3ETyson%20Bateman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20I%20lived%20and%20worked%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-best-food-in-houston-texas-locals-guide-2019-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHouston%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20I%20frequently%20indulged%20in%20food%20from%20the%20Nigerian%20community%20and%20became%20mildly%20addicted%20to%20skewers%20of%20suya%20and%20jollof%20rice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Onwuachi's%20%2463%20chicken%20wasn't%20as%20spicy%20as%20the%20dishes%20at%20the%20mom-and-pop%20restaurants%20I%20used%20to%20frequent%2C%20he%20still%20brought%20some%20heat%20to%20the%20dish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-the-best-roast-chicken-tips-from-chef-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eroasted%20half%20chicken%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20dominated%20the%20plate%20barely%20required%20a%20knife.%20The%20tender%20meat%20was%20rubbed%20in%20a%20paste%20flavored%20with%20an%20earthy%20spice%20mix%20known%20as%20berbere%20and%20crowned%20with%20an%20herb%20salad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rice%20%E2%80%94%20made%20with%20tomatoes%2C%20chiles%2C%20and%20complex%20spices%20%E2%80%94%20tasted%20just%20like%20a%20grandmother's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchefs-go-to-comfort-foods-2019-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomfort%20food%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deceptively%20simple%20dish%20was%20also%20plated%20with%20half%20a%20lime%2C%20more%20berbere%20paste%2C%20and%20a%20sweet-and-creamy%20mix%20of%20ricotta%20and%20honey.%20It%20was%20fun%20to%20mix%20and%20match%20these%20toppings%20to%20make%20each%20bite%20taste%20slightly%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOnwuachi%20recently%20brought%20his%20famous%20oxtails%20back%20to%20the%20menu%2C%20too.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Caribbean-style%20oxtails%20covered%20in%20sauce%20and%20garnished%20with%20greens%20on%20a%20black%20plate.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673bb672192f525898594392%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20dined%20just%20days%20after%20the%20oxtails%20were%20introduced%20to%20the%20menu.%3Cp%3ETyson%20Bateman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Caribbean-style%20oxtails%20that%20Onwuachi%20made%20at%20Kith%2FKin%20returned%20to%20DC%20on%20November%201%2C%20just%20days%20before%20I%20dined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20%2465%2C%20they%20weren't%20cheap%2C%20but%20I%20ordered%20them%20over%20the%20%24110%20wagyu%20short%20rib%20I'd%20been%20considering.%20The%20sugar%20and%20collagen%20in%20the%20sauce%20made%20it%20delightfully%20sticky%20%E2%80%94%20the%20dish%20felt%20like%20a%20beefy%20dessert.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExtracting%20the%20pillowy%20meat%20from%20the%20bones%20reminded%20me%20of%20gamja-tang%2C%20my%20favorite%20Korean%20stew%20made%20from%20a%20pig's%20neck%20bones.%20It%20was%20tougher%20to%20get%20the%20meat%20off%20without%20the%20chopsticks%20or%20gloves%20usually%20provided%20at%20Korean%20restaurants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20did%20my%20best%20to%20finish%20every%20bite%2C%20spooning%20the%20sauce%20over%20the%20coconut-infused%20rice%20and%20peas%20to%20experience%20the%20unique%20flavor%20combination%20of%20sweet%20heat%20and%20flesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20room%20for%20dessert%2C%20but%20I%20ordered%20it%20anyway.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20plate%20of%20rum%20cake%20with%20vanilla%20whip%2C%20mint%20leaves%2C%20and%20cape%20gooseberries.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673bb734ede4eeae3928494b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20rum%20cake%20was%20a%20surprising%20delight.%3Cp%3ETyson%20Bateman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20get%20any%20pressure%20from%20Andrea%20or%20the%20other%20servers%20to%20order%20dessert%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20want%20the%20meal%20to%20end%20just%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20only%20two%20desserts%20on%20the%20menu%2C%20so%20I%20chose%20the%20%2417%20rum%20cake%20over%20the%20spiced%20cherry%20sorbet%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I'm%20glad%20I%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20sweet%20treat%20sounded%20a%20little%20boring%20on%20paper%2C%20the%20crisp%20edges%20and%20fluffy%20center%20of%20the%20two%20slabs%20of%