20the%20country%20should%20keep%20its%20self-respect%20while%20dealing%20with%20the%20matter%2C%20according%20to%20sources.%20Sharif%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20patron-in-chief%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%2C%20also%20told%20Naqvi%20that%20it%20was%20not%20just%20about%20money%20and%20that%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20public%20should%20also%20be%20taken%20into%20consideration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20refused%20to%20play%20its%20Champions%20Trophy%20matches%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20instead%20demanded%20the%20tournament%20be%20played%20in%20a%20'hybrid%20model'%2C%20which%20would%20allow%20it%20to%20play%20its%20matches%20at%20a%20neutral%20venue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20top%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20source%2C%20the%20global%20governing%20body%20for%20the%20sport%20has%20reached%20a%20consensus%20to%20conduct%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20in%20a%20hybrid%20model%2C%20allowing%20India%20to%20play%20its%20share%20of%20matches%20in%20Dubai%20while%20agreeing%20%26quot%3Bin%20principle%26quot%3B%20to%20a%20similar%20arrangement%20in%20multi-lateral%20events%20till%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaqvi%2C%20on%20Sunday%2C%20briefed%20Sharif%20on%20the%20behind-the-scenes%20developments%20but%20the%20PCB%20didn't%20reveal%20details%20of%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Prime%20Minister%20assured%20his%20complete%20support%20to%20the%20PCB%20on%20the%20issue%20and%20appreciated%20the%20stance%20taken%20by%20the%20(PCB)%20chairman%20on%20India%20refusing%20to%20play%20in%20Pakistan%20in%20the%20mega-event%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20Naqvi%20was%20told%20by%20Sharif%20that%20everything%20was%20not%20about%20money%20and%20Pakistan%20should%20deal%20with%20the%20matter%20keeping%20its%20self-respect%20and%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20stance%20adopted%20by%20the%20PCB%20reflects%20the%20feelings%20of%20all%20Pakistanis%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20after%20the%20refusal%20of%20India%20to%20play%20in%20Pakistan%2C%26quot%3B%20Geo%20TV%20quoted%20the%20premier%20as%20telling%20Naqvi%20during%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaqvi%20has%20said%20that%20any%20decision%20on%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20would%20be%20taken%20after%20seeking%20advice%20from%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20source%20close%20to%20the%20government%20said%20that%20Naqvi%20had%20apparently%20met%20the%20PM%20on%20a%20short%20notice%20to%20inform%20him%20about%20Pakistan's%20next%20step%2C%20as%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20board%20was%20not%20willing%20to%20accept%20the%20%26quot%3Bfusion%20formula%26quot%3B%20proposed%20by%20the%20PCB%20to%20the%20ICC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBasically%2C%20Naqvi%20wanted%20to%20keep%20the%20PM%20updated%20and%20get%20his%20approval%20if%20the%20PCB%20decides%20to%20break%20the%20deadlock%20with%20any%20tough%20decision%20on%20the%20tournament%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC%20headquarters%20in%20Dubai%20has%20been%20the%20hub%20of%20discussion%20around%20the%20%26quot%3Bfusion%20formula%26quot%3B%20proposed%20by%20the%20PCB%20on%20the%20hosting%20of%20ICC%20events%20for%20the%20next%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPCB%20wants%20the%20BCCI%20to%20accept%20a%20formula%20under%20which%20if%20India%20does%20not%20play%20any%20ICC%20event%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20the%20neighbouring%20team%20will%20also%20not%20visit%20India%20for%20any%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733651520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fsnovspvg_mohsin-naqvi-x_625x300_19_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fpakistan-pm-jumps-into-icc-champions-trophy-row-with-bcci-assures-pc